data.description: Home is eligible for $5000 towards down payment, closing costs or rate buydowns. This beautiful home offers an open floor plan, modern elegance, and abundant natural light. The gourmet kitchen with granite countertops, spacious living area with 9 ft ceilings, and luxurious master suite are sure to impress. Enjoy outdoor living with a fully fenced backyard and covered patio. Conveniently located near amenities and transportation routes. Don't miss out on this exceptional property!
